<br>
I have a young magician that I am playing on a frequent basis. Level 13 at the moment and enjoying it immensely.<br>
<br>
I have a question though. I seem to remember in a patch that SOE/VI changed it so that pets would always be the strongest when summoned, and certainly for the first couple of circles (4 and 8 ) when summoning the pets at the start of that level (4 or 8 ) they would be conning yellow, as I would expect.<br>
<br>
When I got my level 12 pets, I summoned one to find that it was conning blue... a bit confused, I cleared the spell and re-memorised it to make sure I had picked up the right one (done that too many times) Re-summoned and same deal...<br>
<br>
